title: 2589_CTRL_CAU
characteristics_ch1.7: ethnicity (w: white, b: black, nw: non-white): W
extract_protocol_ch1: RNA was extracted from powdered, frozen brain tissue using standard TRIzol (Invitrogen) extraction method. RNA samples were treated with RQ1 RNase-free DNase (Promega), purified by TRIzol LS (Ambion) and checked on Agilent Bioanalyzer
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Polyadenylated mRNA was collected by Dynabeads mRNA Purification Kit (Ambion). The libraries were prepared by TruSeq RNA Sample Preparation Kit v2 (Illumina) following manufacturer’s instructions. High-throughput sequencing was performed on NovaSeq (Illumina) to obtain 150 nucleotide paired-end reads.
data_processing: Illumina's bcl2fastq2 Conversion Software v2.19 was used for basecalling.
data_processing.1: Salmon quantifications were derived using Salmon (version 0.8.2) from raw FastQ against the hg38 transcriptome sequences retrieved in the Bioconductor TxDb.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg38.knownGene
data_processing.2: Gene expression values (log2-cpm) were generated by edgeR (version 3.36.0) using the cpm function with log = TRUE and prior.count = 3
data_processing.4: Supplementary files format and content: Salmon transcript quantifications against the hg38 transcriptome sequences.
ethnicity..w.ch1: white, b: black, nw: non-white): W
